President Magufuli has unveiled his full cabinet composed of 23 ministers and 23 deputy ministers. The cabinet features old and new faces. The State House Chief Secretary John Kijazi announced names of 21 new ministers and their respective 23 deputies at Chamwino State House, Dodoma on Saturday evening. Prior to the recent nomination, President Magufuli had already appointed two ministers; Dr Philip Mpango (Finance and Planning) and Prof Palamagamba Kabudi (Foreign Affairs and Â East African Cooperation). Full List of ministers and their deputies click here